OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEmiliano Sala: Footballer's
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmother seeks justice,      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Finquest hears              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The mother of footballer Emiliano Sala 
OL,6, has told the inquest into his death    
OL,7, that she wants justice for him and to  
OL,8, prevent future similar deaths.         
OL,10,FThe 28-year-old died in a plane crash  
OL,11,Fin the English Channel in January 2019 
OL,12,Fafter being bought by Cardiff City from
OL,13,FNantes in a #15m transfer deal.        
OL,15,FIn a statement at the hearing, Sala's  
OL,16,Fmother, Mercedes Taffarel, said: "Our  
OL,17,Fpain will never go away. We carry it   
OL,18,Fwith us all the time."                 
OL,20,FThe jury inquest could take five weeks.
